snippet.title: DB Business
snippet.description: This is a channel of DB Business. We are a team of business minded people who love and breathe by technology and innovations, we created this channel to share the most epic and legendary stories about this industry. Also, we love to listen to interviews of people like Steve Jobs, Elon Musk and others. If we listen to something special we love to share them. Do not miss the weekly videos about these epic business and technology stories. We are sure you will learn many things and like it.
